    <p class="caption-helper">Required levels for freshwater fish</p>
        <%= image_tag('helpers/oxygen.jpg', alt: "cycles") %>
    <p class="caption-helper">Dissolved oxygen levels often stratify in the winter and summer, turning over in the spring and fall as lake temperatures align.</p>


  </div>
</div>